# mpesakit

> âš¡ **Effortless M-Pesa integration** using Safaricom's Daraja API â€” built for developers, by developers.

[![Python 3.12+](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.12+-blue.svg)](https://www.python.org/downloads/)
